data.title: ERNEST FLORES, III Obituary 2024

data.text:
Ernie Flores III, 42 years old of Phoenix, AZ, passed away on May 29, 2024. He was born and raised in Phoenix, AZ on January 16, 1982, to his parents Ernest Jr. and Frances.

Ernie is survived by his father Ernie Jr and mother Frances; brother Ceasar Flores; sisters Michelle, Valerie, and Emily; Grandfather George Ybarra; and a special thanks to the Ochoa Family for all the love and support they have provided to the Flores family during this difficult time. Also, a very special thank you to the Phoenix Fire department for the lifetime of mentoring they gave Ernie III. Ernie was loved by all who knew him and will be dearly missed.
